CISSP, CISA or equivalent certification in information security;
Experience in security standards such as ISO 27001, 27002, 27005; NIST, COBIT, ITIL;
Experience in developing corporate policies or guidelines;
Possess breadth of knowledge of IT and information security concepts, practices and standards, networks, data, systems, databases, applications and identities;
